main event: A UFO sighting was reported in Lakehurst, N.J. on August 6, 1957, with objects flashing lights and changing colors.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 5 minutes,1 to 2 objects were observed,The objects were seen directly over one another,The lights emitted by the objects were reported to be flashing and changing colors,The conclusion of the report suggested they were probably meteors.
sighted object: one or two objects with flashing lights
